snippet.title: Withering Rooms - Release Date Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Withering Rooms is a challenging 2.5D horror RPG set in a procedurally generated Victorian mansion that changes each night.  Experience Mostyn House, filled with overgrown undead, invisible ghosts, devious witches, and axe wielding madmen on April 2nd.
